                    "type": "output_text",
                    "text": "{\"summary\": {\"sosovalue\": \"Community sentiment towards SoSoValue is predominantly positive, driven by promotional posts calling it 'the best project,' sharing ETF dashboard updates (e.g., Polkadot TDOT), EXP farming tasks, and Season 2 airdrop reminders. Some promotional spam and one skeptical post questioning reward fairness for high EXP grinders (potential failure if < $5k payout), but overall optimistic with focus on staking, tasks, and ecosystem growth. Low engagement on most posts.\", \"sodex\": \"Mixed but leaning neutral-positive. Users share tier achievements (e.g., Iron tier, SoPoints), trading recaps (e.g., $1M volume, red PnL but still rewarding volume), and refs. Some frustration in non-project contexts (e.g., unrelated replies), but project-related activity promotes participation and airdrops.\", \"ssi\": \"Limited direct mentions, neutral to positive. Posts note SSI Staking Epoch 4 (TVL $98M+, APY 20%+, 487k holders), ssiMAG7 index down 3%, and daily updates. Factual sharing without strong emotional sentiment; tied to SoSoValue ecosystem positively.\"}, \"top_questions\": {\"sosovalue\": [\"Will Season 2 airdrop rewards be fair for high EXP grinders?\", \"How to maximize EXP before snapshot?\", \"Is SoSoValue expanding ETF dashboards effectively?\"], \"sodex\": [\"Are SoPoints still worth farming post zero-fee end?\", \"How to rank higher in SoDEX leaderboards?\", \"Sodex global launch impact on $SOSO?\"], \"ssi\": [\"SSI Staking Epoch 4 APY sustainable?\", \"What caused ssiMAG7 3% drop?\", \"SSI Index correlation to broader market?\"]}, \"post_links\": [\"https://x.com/DahiruAbdu97205/status/2030351603589402910\", \"https://x.com/AriWalletPlus/status/2030158374726488405\", \"https://x.com/Gloriousmylve/status/2030351223874810251\", \"https://x.com/sodex_001/status/2030350392521859389\", \"https://x.com/BillurCabuk/status/2030258384549675497\", \"https://x.com/CGS_Tribe/status/2030168444159627544\", \"https://x.com/Nik